Present your app to users on Google Play

Make a great first impression and help users find and engage with your app through your store listing. Edit information like your app's name, icon, description, screenshots and video to increase discoverability and drive downloads.

Graphics

Manage your app icon, screenshots and videos to promote your app on Google Play. Review the content guidelines before uploading new graphics. If you add translations for your Store Listing without localised graphics, we will use the graphics from your default language.

error
Image dimensions must be 512 px by 512 px
Upload an icon

Your app icon must be a PNG or JPEG, up to 1 MB, 512 px by 512 px, and meet our design specifications and metadata policy

 
Drop a PNG or JPEG file here to upload

Your feature graphic must be a PNG or JPEG, up to 15 MB and 1,024 px by 500 px

 

Add a video by entering a YouTube URL. This video must be public or unlisted, ads must be turned off, it must not be age-restricted and it should be landscape.
